channel.description: Math.max The general syntax for this method is: Math.max(x, y, z, ...) This method finds and returns the largest value from a set of numbers (x, y, z, â€¦). To find the maximum value in an array, see below. Example console.log(Math.max(2, 3, 100.01, 0, -5.2, 100));
